    "description":  "Use this service to apply for a building assessment certificate from the Building Safety Regulator.",
    "details":  {
                    "attachments":  [

                                    ],
                    "body":  "\u003cdiv class=\"govspeak\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eUse this service to apply for a building assessment certificate (\u003cabbr title=\"building assessment certificate\"\u003eBAC\u003c/abbr\u003e) if:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eyou are the principal accountable person of a registered high-rise residential building\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ethe Building Safety Regulator (\u003cabbr title=\"Building Safety Regulator\"\u003eBSR\u003c/abbr\u003e) has told you to apply for a \u003cabbr title=\"building assessment certificate\"\u003eBAC\u003c/abbr\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eHigh-rise residential buildings are known as higher-risk buildings under the Building Safety Act 2022. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Warning\" class=\"application-notice help-notice\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYou must submit your BAC application within 28 calendar days of BSR telling you to apply.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"before-you-start\"\u003eBefore you start\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eRead the guide about \u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/preparing-a-building-assessment-certificate-application\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003epreparing a building assessment certificate application.\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eTo apply for a \u003cabbr title=\"building assessment certificate\"\u003eBAC\u003c/abbr\u003e, you’ll need to:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003econfirm the information \u003cabbr title=\"Building Safety Regulator\"\u003eBSR\u003c/abbr\u003e holds is up to date\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eupload your \u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/preparing-a-safety-case-report\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003esafety case report\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eupload information about your \u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/operating-a-mandatory-occurrence-reporting-system\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003emandatory occurrence reporting system\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eupload your \u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/preparing-a-resident-engagement-strategy\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eresident engagement strategy\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eprovide serial numbers of any compliance notices issued by \u003cabbr title=\"Building Safety Regulator\"\u003eBSR\u003c/abbr\u003e that are currently in force\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003econfirm that you, and any other accountable persons for the building are \u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/high-rise-residential-building-information-accountable-persons-must-provide\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eproviding building information to relevant individuals and organisations\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou’ll need to provide payment card or invoice details to pay:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ethe application charge of £288 (including VAT)\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003efor the work done by \u003cabbr title=\"Building Safety Regulator\"\u003eBSR\u003c/abbr\u003e to assess the application as set out in the \u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.hse.gov.uk/building-safety/charging-scheme.htm\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003e\u003cabbr title=\"Building Safety Regulator\"\u003eBSR\u003c/abbr\u003e charging scheme\u003c/a\u003e on the \u003cabbr title=\"Health and Safety Executive\"\u003eHSE\u003c/abbr\u003e website\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou can provide a purchase order number if you need it on the invoices.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca class=\"gem-c-button govuk-button govuk-button--start\" role=\"button\" data-module=\"govuk-button\" data-ga4-attributes=\u0027{\"event_name\":\"navigation\",\"type\":\"start button\"}\u0027 draggable=\"false\" href=\"https://register-high-rise-building.hse.gov.uk/returning-application\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e Start now \u003c/span\u003e\u003csvg class=\"govuk-button__start-icon govuk-!-display-none-print\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"17.5\" height=\"19\" viewbox=\"0 0 33 40\" focusable=\"false\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cpath fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M0 0h13l20 20-20 20H0l20-20z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"if-you-need-help-using-this-service\"\u003eIf you need help using this service\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/contact-building-safety-regulator\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eContact \u003cabbr title=\"Building Safety Regulator\"\u003eBSR\u003c/abbr\u003e\u003c/a\u003e if you need help with your application.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e",
